::Kluster::

Kluster nearly crashes into Blur on his way out. "I'm here. If you could 
follow me for a second, I'd be most greatful," he says to the new Maximal, 
setting off toward Phobia's ship.

"You can expect two bots," he says into his comm-link to Phobia.
